1
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,080
Don’t always

2
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,250
lock yourself in Palace of Eternal Peace.

3
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,800
When you’re free,

4
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,520
go to Palace of Eternal Spring for a visit.

5
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,780
And come to the garden too to look around.

6
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,880
But you must instruct your servants

7
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,470
that you must be accompanied.

8
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,080
Your Majesty,

9
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,130
I will never be able to repay you

10
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,360
for your grace.

11
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,200
I am the Empress.

12
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,720
It's my duty to take care of the imperial harem.

13
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,380
You don’t need to be grateful.

14
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,440
If everyone in the Palace

15
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:32,000
could be as magnanimous as Your Majesty,

16
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,800
there wouldn't be so many conflicts.

17
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,560
Consort Yu,

18
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,720
no need to be too fearful.

19
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,880
In this world,

20
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,160
if there are good people,

21
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,960
there are bad people.

22
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:49,480
As long as you keep a usual mind,

23
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,780
in that case...

24
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,000
Empress!

25
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,760
What's wrong?

26
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,360
Snowball!

27
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,560
Empress, look at how adorable Snowball is.

28
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,520
It’s humanized.

29
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,720
Reward!

30
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,200
Your Majesty, I'm afraid of dogs.

31
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,460
I'll take my leave now.

32
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,360
Empress,

33
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,240
Her Majesty is here with Consort Yu.

34
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,960
Escort Consort Yu back.

35
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,000
Yes.

36
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,080
Thank you, Your Majesty.

37
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,210
I will take my leave.

38
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,600
Wait!

39
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,480
How come you are rushing to leave

40
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,480
after seeing me?

41
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,200
I am not a tiger.

42
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,079
You think I'll bite?

43
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,050
Noble Consort Empress.

44
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,890
Greetings to you, Noble Consort Empress.

45
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,160
Your Majesty.

46
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,210
Consort Yu is not feeling well.

47
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,690
We should let her go back for a rest.

48
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,760
I have to say,

49
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,480
Your Majesty,

50
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:04,410
you have gathered quite a strange lot around you.

51
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:07,080
Either they are so cowardly like a mouse,

52
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,000
or they are so bold as to be afraid of nothing.

53
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,400
How weird is that?

54
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,760
Sister Yu,

55
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,760
stay with us and watch Snowball perform.

56
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:19,880
It's fun.

57
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,760
Empress,

58
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,640
I'm not feeling well. I'll take my leave.

59
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,920
- Don’t come here! - Consort Yu!

60
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,850
Don’t come here!

61
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,260
Get rid of that dog!

62
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,810
Don’t come here!

63
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:36,900
Go away!

64
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,600
Go away! Go away!

65
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,080
Go!

66
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:39,840
Go!

67
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,800
Consort Yu!

68
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,200
What's to fear about a bad dog?

69
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,060
Come over here!

70
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,120
Wei Yingluo,

71
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,680
how dare you!

72
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:54,290
You dare hurt the favorite dog of Noble Consort Empress?

73
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:57,040
Check if it’s hurt.

74
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,080
Empress.

75
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:58,640
How is it?

76
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,280
Empress,

77
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,520
it has a huge swelling on its abdomen.

78
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,760
You low-down servant

79
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,960
dared hurt my beloved dog.

80
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,800
You’ll pay with your life.

81
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,100
Noble Consort Gao,

82
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,080
I did all that

83
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,960
for your sake.

84
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,960
Nonsense!

85
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,040
You hurt my beloved pet

86
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,320
and you dare to quibble?

87
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:29,800
Consort Yu

88
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,880
is pregnant with the Emperor’s offspring.

89
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,440
She's especially valuable now.

90
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,520
If your beloved dog

91
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:37,159
harmed the offspring in Consort Yu's womb,

92
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,340
and if anything bad happened,

93
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,159
some inconsiderate persons

94
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:44,680
might accuse you of attempting to murder the Emperor’s offspring.

95
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,720
I dare them?

96
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,240
Rumors are more ferocious than a tiger.

97
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,320
There are so many inconsiderate people.

98
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:54,560
They are always bumping on others for no reason.

99
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,290
If you get hurt because of it, it would be not good.

100
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,720
So,

101
00:05:58,960 --> 00:05:59,800
earlier,

102
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,760
I kicked off that bad dog.

103
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,960
I eliminated the possible disasters that might befall you.

104
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,680
Although I was a bit reckless,

105
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,080
I preserved your reputation.

106
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,240
You…

107
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,680
Just now,

108
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,600
I saw that dog was behaving well.

109
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,440
How come

110
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,260
it suddenly created a ruckus?

111
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,760
If my guess is right,

112
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,360
I heard this dog

113
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,130
barking wildly.

114
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,680
Go check

115
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,200
if anything is wrong with it.

116
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,480
Empress,

117
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,220
I didn't find anything wrong.

118
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:49,600
Should we take it back to our palace and do a thorough check?

119
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,360
Who dares?

120
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:56,080
If anyone hurts my beloved dog by a hair,

121
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,760
I will tear her apart.

122
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,570
Your Majesty, Noble Consort Empress,

123
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:10,520
they say that dogs have natural instincts to defend their masters.

124
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:13,320
They chase after villains as soon as they see them.

125
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,920
So I'm guessing

126
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,360
maybe it was because

127
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,160
Consort Yu was leaving in a rush,

128
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,280
and Snowball misunderstood it.

129
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,200
Sister Yu,

130
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,840
are you alright?

131
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,160
Thank you for your concerns, Consort Jia.

132
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,560
Consort Yu just got scared and will be fine.

133
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,480
You reacted very fast.

134
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,200
You're more nimble than a dog.

135
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:38,960
Thank you for your praises, Consort Jia.

136
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,600
Escort Consort Yu back to Palace of Eternal Peace.

137
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,520
Yes.

138
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,640
Noble Consort,

139
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,040
Yingluo was right.

140
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:05,280
If today your beloved dog

141
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,560
hurt Consort Yu,

142
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,000
this matter

143
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,260
will surely raise a colossal uproar.

144
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,480
In my opinion,

145
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:18,640
you need to watch over people around you.

146
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:22,080
If they keep being this incompetent,

147
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,840
can't even keep watch of one dog

148
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,640
and create troubles again,

149
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:29,840
I won't tolerate it.

150
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,850
Consort Jia,

151
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,200
how have I treated you?

152
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,680
I came from

153
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,760
a lowly family.

154
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,300
Fourth Prince is not favored.

155
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,520
Without your care,

156
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,920
my son and I

157
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,860
wouldn't have a place to stand in the Palace.

158
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:04,440
I've always liked your intelligence and quick wit.

159
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,640
Whenever I see any benefit,

160
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,370
I will think of you and your son.

161
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,780
I never mistreated you even a bit.

162
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:11,920
Yes.

163
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,400
I will forever remember your grace.

164
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:22,840
Who told you to betray me?

165
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:25,280
Who told you to use Snowball to harm Consort Yu?

166
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,680
Who gave you the courage?

167
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,080
Noble Consort Empress...

168
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,080
I did that...

169
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,240
I did that

170
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,880
for your sake!

171
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,800
For my sake?

172
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,680
No.

173
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:43,160
You did that for your Fourth Prince.

174
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:48,060
You're afraid that Consort Yu may give birth to a prince

175
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,300
and disturb your beautiful plan.

176
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:52,850
Empress,

177
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:53,960
yes,

178
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:56,320
I indeed am afraid

179
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,380
Consort Yu may give birth to a prince.

180
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,520
But I really did that

181
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,880
for your sake!

182
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:04,120
Empress, you failed in the previous plan

183
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,320
and incurred hatred of Palace of Eternal Peace.

184
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,640
If we don't completely sever this hope of Consort Yu,

185
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,560
we may have unending future troubles!

186
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,720
Please believe me!

187
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,280
Were you really thinking

188
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,840
a dog

189
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,760
could seriously harm someone?

190
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,920
You are right.

191
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:27,000
How could I be that stupid?

192
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:33,840
Snowball is just a start.

193
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:35,840
Empress,

194
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,720
just wait to see a good show.

195
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,400
Consort Yu.

196
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,320
Her Majesty gave me some instructions.

197
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,080
She said that the pearl powder she gave you last time

198
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,480
should have been used up.

199
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,380
She told me to deliver some today.

200
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:18,200
Yingluo,

201
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,730
you're here.

202
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,240
These days,

203
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,360
you helped a lot.

204
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:28,880
After getting traumatized by that bad dog, Consort kept having nightmares.

205
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:31,480
She needs to take in nerve-calming pills before she can sleep.

206
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:34,040
But the imperial doctor said it's bad for the Emperor’s offspring,

207
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,440
so she mustn't take much.

208
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,240
Fortunately we have the pearl power

209
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,100
Her Majesty has been delivering.

210
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:42,380
Or else, the illness of Consort Yu would have worsened.

211
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,450
Fangcao, what's wrong with your hand?

212
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:51,120
When I was preparing the pearl balls for Consort,

213
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,720
I touched some of the powder.

214
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,180
I'll go wash it off.

215
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,360
Repeat your words.

216
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,320
Yingluo, what's wrong?

217
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,480
I told you to repeat your words!

218
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:10,600
Consort.

219
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,440
Yingluo,

220
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,760
what's wrong?

221
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:16,660
Consort, look.

222
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:19,480
The color of pearl powder is white.

223
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:23,700
The powder on the nails of Fangcao is clearly light yellow.

224
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:26,020
This is not the color of pearl powder.

225
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:28,760
Fangcao,

226
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,720
what did you put

227
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,120
in the pearl balls you prepared?

228
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,720
I don't know why.

229
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:38,360
The pearl powder was sent by Her Majesty.

230
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,120
This is your plan.

231
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,220
Consort Yu,

232
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,760
this is the pearl powder

233
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:48,220
delivered by Her Majesty.

234
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,720
Look. Is it of the same color with the powder

235
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,640
on her nails?

236
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,720
Look.

237
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:04,640
These pearl balls are white on the outside.

238
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:27,760
The powder inside

239
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,240
shimmers in the light.

240
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:33,120
This is not pearl powder.

241
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,560
I'm not an imperial doctor.

242
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:41,840
I don’t know what it is.

243
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,480
Pearl powder

244
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,240
doesn’t shimmer.

245
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:51,320
Shell powder does.

246
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:53,850
Fangcao,

247
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,440
why did you replace the pearl powder

248
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,560
delivered by Her Majesty?

249
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,840
I was wrong!

250
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:04,200
My mother

251
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:05,680
is sick.

252
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,600
We didn’t have enough money for her treatment.

253
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,240
I didn’t know what to do.

254
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:13,240
I knew shell powder was cheap

255
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,970
and pearl powder was valuable,

256
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,400
so I stole the pearl powder

257
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,240
and traded it for money.

258
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:23,200
Consort,

259
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:26,240
I have meticulously cared for you.

260
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,200
Please spare me.

261
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:31,480
Fangcao,

262
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,220
you've been serving me for so many years.

263
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,000
If you told me that your mother was sick,

264
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,320
you think I wouldn’t help?

265
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,640
I was muddled.

266
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:40,960
Consort,

267
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,680
I won't do it again.

268
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,560
Even you would do such a thing!

269
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,160
I’m disappointed.

270
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:49,000
Please forgive me, Consort.

271
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:53,080
I will do everything I could to repay you in the rest of my life.

272
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,680
Fangcao has served me for so many years.

273
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,200
She probably didn't mean to hurt me.

274
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,240
We may let it go this time.

275
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:08,410
Consort, don't believe her so easily.

276
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,090
Replacing pearl powder

277
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,370
with cheap shell powder

278
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:15,640
might look like theft.

279
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,880
Shell powder is yellow.

280
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:22,320
Then the balls can’t appear pure white.

281
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,760
But the shell powder balls Fangcao gave you

282
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:26,420
are snow white on the outside.

283
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,880
The shimmering powder is limited to the inside.

284
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:31,940
We can’t see the difference unless the ball is crashed.

285
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,720
What did you add in it?

286
