00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:44,080
and no one has discovered it.

568
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:49,000
Our Snowball just barked a few times

569
00:29:49,320 --> 00:29:51,520
and she got scared like that.

570
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,400
She's useless.

571
00:29:54,120 --> 00:29:55,600
First, Consort Yi died.

572
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:58,280
Then, she was almost killed.

573
00:29:59,080 --> 00:30:00,810
Plus Snowball's provocation,

574
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,480
she surely would be seriously scared.

575
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,520
I think

576
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:07,010
she won't even dare go to the Imperial Garden.

577
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,560
What else did she say?

578
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:13,480
Fangcao said

579
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,660
the shell powder you gave her was almost used up.

580
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:17,960
She needed some more.

581
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:21,280
I promised her that after reporting it to you,

582
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:23,140
I would quickly deliver it to her.

583
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:25,280
Go ahead. Be careful.

584
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,040
Yes.

585
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,000
Wait.

586
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:33,640
Empress, do you have more instructions?

587
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:36,640
You said Consort Yu had serious abdominal pain.

588
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:39,600
She said that Consort Yu had frequent severe abdominal pains.

589
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:41,480
They asked Director Zhang of Imperial Hospital to check her.

590
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:44,760
He prescribed pregnancy preserving medicine and didn't notice anything wrong.

591
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:46,560
He thought that it was caused by psychological trauma.

592
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:49,160
The dosage of pearl powder was also increased.

593
00:30:49,760 --> 00:30:51,440
Her symptoms are so obvious?

594
00:30:52,520 --> 00:30:53,980
That's what Fangcao said.

595
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:56,440
If you have no more additional instructions,

596
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:58,480
I'll go deliver her shell powder.

597
00:30:59,560 --> 00:31:00,360
Wait.

598
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,900
Tell her that shell powder

599
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:09,240
must be meticulously made.

600
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,640
We still need two more days to prepare it.

601
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,800
Tell her to meet you

602
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:16,560
during the lychee party.

603
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:18,640
But

604
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:21,000
we have shell powder.

605
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:22,200
Just do as I said.

606
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,040
Yes.

607
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:32,720
What's wrong?

608
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:46,690
Yingluo,

609
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:49,040
why don't we pick the fruit now,

610
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:51,560
clean them, and deliver them during the lychee party?

611
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:52,400
Master told me

612
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:54,740
to pick them on site tomorrow,

613
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,980
so they would be fresh.

614
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:03,120
I also want to taste these lychees.

615
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:06,520
Too bad

616
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,380
each of them has been assigned

617
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,960
to a specific consort.

618
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:12,740
This is the yearly tribute of Fujian.

619
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:14,460
Certainly they are precious.

620
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,730
If you really want to eat it,

621
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,530
after you get out of the palace,

622
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:22,680
you can go to Fujian by a boat.

623
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:25,200
Eat as much as you want.

624
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,600
Isn't that more fun?

625
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:29,760
That’s a bold idea!

626
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,130
You can leave them to me.

627
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,240
I'll verify it again.

628
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:51,960
Yingluo.

629
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:55,480
Yingluo,

630
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,640
you said that as long as I make up for what I did,

631
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,960
I will be forgiven.

632
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:00,160
Is that true?

633
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,170
You have my word.

634
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:05,960
Consort Jia said she'd let Ah-Shuang

635
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:07,960
give me some shell powder tomorrow.

636
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:11,680
You only said Consort Yu was taking in pearl powder

637
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,490
and didn't mention anything else?

638
00:33:14,840 --> 00:33:16,160
You didn't add any more details?

639
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,360
Add any more details?

640
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,200
No.

641
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,880
You are too eager to make up for what you did.

642
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:23,010
Too much is as bad as too little.

643
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:26,200
Don't worry. I surely didn't make any mistake.

644
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:28,360
But you must do as you said.

645
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:29,320
Ok.

646
00:33:31,320 --> 00:33:32,980
I'll report it to Her Majesty.

647
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,360
We’ll catch the turtle in the jar.

648
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,680
Ungrateful.

649
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:45,080
Don't you remember how much Empress helped you

650
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:46,280
when you were in need?

651
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,640
Forget it.

652
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:50,920
Empress, how can we forget it?

653
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,400
When Consort Ying had such austere days,

654
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:55,720
you gave her half of your allowance.

655
00:33:55,840 --> 00:33:58,040
You didn't even forget to send her food.

656
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:00,040
Why is it so hard

657
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,380
to ask her for help?

658
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,800
Zhen'er, stop it.

659
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,760
Consort Chun, this is...

660
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:17,800
Sister, you're going everywhere to borrow money.

661
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:19,320
But most people you helped

662
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:21,320
are of a lower rank.

663
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,760
Even if they want to help, they are not able to do it.

664
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,090
Other consorts hate you

665
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:29,980
because you have an illustrious and respected name in the Palace.

666
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,280
They surely will not support you.

667
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:33,670
I think

668
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,480
after being refused

669
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,920
for three days,

670
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:38,690
you should know what to do.

671
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:40,440
So

672
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:42,880
I bring you some money.

673
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:46,670
Empress, you don't need to worry about it anymore.

674
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:47,670
We now have money.

675
00:34:48,230 --> 00:34:49,030
Consort Chun,

676
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:51,000
what do you mean

677
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:52,960
by giving this money?

678
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:55,159
Sister, don't worry.

679
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:57,210
I’m not like Noble Consort Gao.

680
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,960
I won’t require you to disobey your heart

681
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,360
and harm other people.

682
00:35:05,680 --> 00:35:08,120
But from the moment I accept this money,

683
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:10,890
I will never have my own stand anymore.

684
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:12,600
I must always

685
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:15,160
stand on the side of Her Majesty.

686
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:17,160
Her Majesty is virtuous, wise, and magnanimous.

687
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:18,420
She's kind and gentle.

688
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,530
Why can’t you stand on her side?

689
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:24,640
When people are caught in the whirlpool of fighting,

690
00:35:24,640 --> 00:35:26,360
they will just keep falling deeper.

691
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:29,160
It will be harder and harder to differentiate right and wrong.

692
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:31,220
They will keep lowering their limit.

693
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:34,240
In the end, when left with no other choice,

694
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,500
they will harm others.

695
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:38,840
So the day I entered the Palace, I swore

696
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:41,740
I would never get involved in any fights.

697
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:43,960
I'll only guard my Hall of Receiving Celestial FavorPalace of Receiving Celestial Favor

698
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:45,420
and spend my days quietly.

699
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,620
If I accept your offer,

700
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:50,780
that's going against my initial intention.

701
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,600
But you need money, don’t you?

702
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,600
Yes.

703
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:57,080
Changshou is in prison,

704
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,700
waiting for me to save him.

705
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:01,740
Sister, we entered the palace together.

706
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:04,080
We've accompanied each other for so many years.

707
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,600
Let’s count it as a loan.

708
00:36:06,640 --> 00:36:08,360
I would return it to you twice the amount.

709
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,080
No,

710
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:10,360
three times.

711
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,200
Is that ok?

712
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:13,960
Sister,

713
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,820
what I'm lending you is not money,

714
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:18,760
but favor.

715
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,600
If you insist on refusing it,

716
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,560
I can only apologize.

717
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,920
Empress, we can't delay any more.

718
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:31,560
Otherwise, Young Master will be dead.

719
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:34,760
No.

720
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:37,460
I can't take it.

721
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:38,840
Empress!

722
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,240
Yuhu,

723
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:47,240
let's go.

724
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:55,530
Imperial Consort Chun!

725
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,120
Imperial Consort Chun!

726
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:58,450
Imperial Consort Chun!

727
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,970
Empress, what should we do now?

728
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:11,360
Imperial Consort Xian is really a wooden-head.

729
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,690
No one can persuade her.

730
00:37:13,720 --> 00:37:15,450
Go to Palace of Eternal Spring.

731
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:17,240
It's late.

732
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:19,770
Why are you going to Palace of Eternal Spring?

733
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,080
Let's go.

734
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:35,200
Greetings to you, Your Majesty!

735
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,360
Forego the formalities.

736
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,540
Everyone, please take a seat.

737
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:55,360
Fujian offered some lychees as tribute.

738
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,440
In this tea party,

739
00:37:57,960 --> 00:38:00,600
we’ll have a taste of them.

740
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:06,720
His Majesty loves Her Majesty so much.

741
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:09,920
I haven't seen even one lychee,

742
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:11,720
but he sent you the trees.

743
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,880
It's not the first time

744
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:16,840
His Majesty has shown how much he loves Her Majesty.

745
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:19,360
Noble Consort Gao, you're not used to it?

746
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:24,280
Where are the lychees?

747
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,540
Noble Consort Gao, a moment, please.

748
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:30,400
Lychees can cause excessive internal heat.

749
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:34,120
Let's drink some light chrysanthemum tea first.

750
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,000
Help yourselves.

751
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,400
Sister Nalan,

752
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:50,520
are lychees really that precious?

753
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:51,680
Certainly.

754
00:38:52,240 --> 00:38:54,040
They are transported here from Fujian

755
00:38:54,040 --> 00:38:56,170
after crossing mountains and waters.

756
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:59,440
I heard that a lot of lychees have fallen off

757
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,520
because they are not used to the new environment.

758
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:02,960
The rest will be distributed

759
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:05,960
to Empress Dowager, Her Majesty, and the concubines.

760
00:39:06,200 --> 00:39:09,080
And those highly-favored officials and relatives.

761
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,880
It’ll be a great fortune

762
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:12,960
if we can eat one.

763
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:47,890
You dare secretly switch the pearl powder of Consort Yu?

764
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,760
You're attempting to kill the Emperor’s offspring.

765
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,690
What did you say?

766
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,850
You are a close maid of Consort Jia.

767
00:39:53,080 --> 00:39:54,540
If we catch you doing that,

768
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,140
Consort Jia can't escape.

769
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:58,920
At this point,

770
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,610
what else do you have to say?

771
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:02,580
Sorry, Sister Ah-Shuang.

772
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:04,810
I've told them everything.

773
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:09,080
You think

774
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:10,720
Consort Jia ordered me

775
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,960
to switch the pearl powder of Consort Yu?

776
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:13,840
Isn't that so?

777
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:16,810
This is a blessing pouch

778
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:19,120
Consort Jia made

779
00:40:19,640 --> 00:40:21,120
for the future prince.

780
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:24,800
It only has some fragrant herbs inside.

781
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,690
Impossible.

782
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:30,800
How come?

783
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:32,840
Consort Jia is really vigilant.

784
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:34,560
She already prepared for this.

785
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:35,360
Wei Yingluo,

786
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:37,560
if you have no evidence,

787
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:38,840
don't make irresponsible remarks.

788
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,520
When you walk at night too often,

789
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:41,920
you’ll bump into a ghost.

790
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,320
You've escaped this time.

791
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,520
What about next time?

792
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,040
You...

793
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:47,720
Wei Yingluo!

794
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:49,720
Don't go!

795
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:50,820
Explain yourself!

796
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:52,320
What's there to explain?

797
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,200
You tried to catch me for no reason.

798
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:55,930
Don't you need to explain that?

799
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:57,760
Did I hit you

800
00:40:58,120 --> 00:40:59,480
or did I tie you up?

801
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,560
You didn't use force,

802
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:03,080
but you slandered me.

803
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:05,000
You must apologize to me.

804
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:05,920
Also,

805
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:08,130
you must apologize to Consort Jia.

806
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:15,900
Why are you trying to trap me here?

807
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,800
We need to talk about it, of course.

808
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,720
Consort Jia asked you to draw me away.

809
00:41:19,720 --> 00:41:21,780
Now, you're trying to delay the time.

810
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,140
What are you planning?

811
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:25,240
What do you mean, draw you away?

812
00:41:25,240 --> 00:41:26,880
You followed me here.

813
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:28,740
You falsely accused me first.

814
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,720
Wei Yingluo!

815
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,320
Wei Yingluo, you're a coward!

816
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,600
You don’t even dare talk to me!

817
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:34,400
Wei Yingluo!

818
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:39,280
Fence sitter!

819
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:41,160
I'll get even with you later.

820
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:51,720
Consort Jia has noticed something was wrong.

821
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:54,120
Why did she ask Fangcao to meet her servant?

822
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,160
Unless...

823
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,770
Why are you running around?

824
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,080
Empress, don't worry.

825
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,650
Everything is in place.

826
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:45,610
I won't ever see that low-down servant again, will I?

827
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,680
I promise

828
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,120
she won’t bother you again.

